{"word":"G4704 - σπουδάζω - spoudázō - spoo-dad'-zo - Do diligence","slug":"G4704","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σπουδάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>spoudázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>spoo-dad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Do diligence"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x03B4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - spoudazo&#x0304;</b> - <i>spoo-dad'-zo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4710\">G4710</a>; to <i>use speed</i>, that is, to <i>make effort</i>, <i>be prompt</i> or <i>earnest:</i> - do (give) diligence, be diligent (forward), endeavour, labour, study."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4705\">G4705</a>, <a href=\"#/G4706\">G4706</a>, <a href=\"#/G4707\">G4707</a>, <a href=\"#/G4708\">G4708</a>, <a href=\"#/G4709\">G4709</a>, <a href=\"#/G4710\">G4710</a>"}]}